programme.title: Live Ryder Cup Golf
programme.desc: Coverage of the third and final day at Le Golf National near Paris, featuring the singles matches between Team Europe and Team USA. The 12 matchplay contests often produce a wealth of drama and quality golf, but at the tournament in Minnesota two years ago the Europeans entered the final day trailing by three points, and were unable to overcome the deficit. Henrik Stenson secured an impressive victory over Jordan Spieth, and Thomas Pieters became the first European rookie to score four points as he triumphed over JB Holmes, but the Americans proved to be the dominant team and won the session 7.5-4.5, to clinch the Ryder Cup by an overall score of 17-11.

The 12 matchplay contests often produce a wealth of drama and quality golf, but at the tournament in Minnesota two years ago the Europeans entered the final day trailing by three points, and were unable to overcome the deficit. Henrik Stenson secured an impressive victory over Jordan Spieth, and Thomas Pieters became the first European rookie to score four points as he triumphed over JB Holmes, but the Americans proved to be the dominant team and won the session 7.5-4.5, to clinch the Ryder Cup by an overall score of 17-11.

programme.title: Ryder Cup Golf
programme.desc: A replay of the third and final day at Le Golf National near Paris, featuring the singles matches between Team Europe and Team USA. The 12 matchplay contests often produce a wealth of drama and quality golf, but at the tournament in Minnesota two years ago the Europeans entered the final day trailing by three points, and were unable to overcome the deficit. Henrik Stenson secured an impressive victory over Jordan Spieth, and Thomas Pieters became the first European rookie to score four points as he triumphed over JB Holmes, but the Americans proved to be the dominant team and won the session 7.5-4.5, to clinch the Ryder Cup by an overall score of 17-11.
